Following the address to the nation by President Cyril Ramaphosa on Saturday, 15 August 2020, on progress in the national effort to contain the COVID-19 pandemic; Ministers who serve in the National Coronavirus Command Council brief the media on the regulations relating to the COVID-19 Level 2 restrictions. The Minister of Cooperative Governance and Traditional Affairs, Dr Nkosazana Dlamini Zuma leads the briefing. 